    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, ready for many more miles. It drives beautifully and has been well cared for, so it\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something dependable and fun to drive. I'd love for someone to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come check it out and see for yourself!",
