    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox delivering power to the rear wheels through a mechanical variable M differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS service and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration, maintaining excellent damping characteristics and turn-in precision. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping remain exceptionally sharp for a driver-focused enthusiast.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
