    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that balances everyday utility with premium comfort. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, expected signs of road use such as light stone chips on the front fascia. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curbing. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seating surfaces are supple and show minimal wear on the bolsters. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and navigation, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, consistent power, supported by a comprehensive service history. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Recent maintenance includes a full fluid flush and a fresh set of high-performance tires with ample tread remaining. This is a dependable, honest car that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
